author: Discovery
description:
Over the course of several weeks, 10 racers conquered bounty holes, knockout races, sand drags, and bounty courses to compete in the first-ever Mud Cup Invitational. One lucky racer will be crowned the champion and win over $100,000 in prizes on the season finale of #MudMadness.
